Alexander F. THOMAS, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1936 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 27, 2018 EMAS, LUCK and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of habeas corpus, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
